<html>
	<body style="font-size: 18px; font-family: verdana; width:700px;">
		
		<table>
			<tr>
				<td>
					$user.firstName,
				</td>
				<td>&nbsp;</td>
			</tr>	
			<tr>
				<td>
					$leader.fullName has invited you to join ScoutTrax.
				</td>	
				<td style="padding: 20px;margin:20px 0 0 20px; background: #D44B38; border: 1px solid #C43B28; color: #FFF; font-weight: bold;">
					<a style="text-decoration: none;color:white;" href="http://www.scouttrax.org/verify.html?userId=$userIdKey&passcode=$passcode">
					Click to learn more about ScoutTrax</a>
				</td>
			</tr>	
			<tr>
				<td colspan='2' style="padding:20px">	
					ScoutTrax is an online scout tracking system. It will help coordinate your scout units progress toward scouting goals and ideals.  
					<p>As a new member of ScoutTrax, you will be able to create your own user name and password.</p>
					
					<p style="color: red;">In order to get started you need to click on the ScoutTrax image below and set up a username and password.</p>
					<a href="http://www.scouttrax.org/verify.html?userId=$userIdKey&passcode=$passcode">		
						<img alt="Click here to go to the scouttrax.org login page" src="http://www.scouttrax.org/images/TraxEmailLink.gif">
					</a>
					<p>After doing this, login and update your information and scout advancement records. 
					This information will be kept secure, while shared with other scout leaders.</p>
				</td>						
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan='2' style="padding:20px">
					If you're not able to access ScoutTrax or have any questions, please contact $leader.fullName at $leader.phone or email $leader.email.
				</td>	
			</tr>
		</table>
	</body>
